andriasang.com/con2j5/ff_ultimate_box_game_list/|title=Full Final Fantasy 25th Anniversary Ultimate Box Game List|publisher=Andriasang|author=Gantayat, Anoop|date=2012-08-31|accessdate=2012-09-02|archive-date=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BUsWxSXQ?url=http://andriasang.com/con2j5/ff_ultimate_box_game_list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

