《最终幻想XII》日本首周销量超过176.4万，相当于《[[最终幻想X|最终幻想X]]》首周销量<ref>{{cite web| author=Jenkins, David| date=2006-03-24| title=Japanese Sales Charts, Week Ending March 19| publisher=[[Media_Create|Media Create]]| url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=8671| accessdate=2006-08-14| archive-date=2011-08-02| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60eIIhaVs?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=8671| dead-url=no}}</ref>。据史克威尔艾尼克斯的会议报告称，《最终幻想XII》发售两周后销量达238万<ref>{{cite web| date=2006-05-24| title=Square Enix Conference Report| publisher=RPGFan| url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1287.html| accessdate=2006-09-01| archive-date=2006-09-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060908020431/http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1287.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。北美版《最终幻想XII》首周出货约150万<ref>{{cite web| date=2006-11-06| title=Square Enix Announces Record Shipment With Final Fantasy XII| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| url=http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2006/1106_1/| accessdate=2006-11-07| archive-date=2011-08-02| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60eIMMWY9?url=http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2006/1106_1/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏到2007年3月时，全球出货超过520万<ref name="sqex07profile">{{cite web|url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/common/images/sqex_07profile_e.pdf#page=6|date=October 2007|accessdate=2008-04-28|publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]|format=PDF|title=2007 profile|page=6|archive-date=2009-04-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5g3aMd1Dx?url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/common/images/sqex_07profile_e.pdf#page=6|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏是2006年全球第四畅销PlayStation 2游戏<ref>{{cite web | publisher=IGN | year=2006 | title=PS2 2006 Year in Review | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/749/749553p2.html | accessdate=2006-03-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080926001250/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/749/749553p2.html | archive-date=2008-09-26 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。PS2版本全球累計銷量為606萬套<ref name="sale"/><ref name="sale_I"/>。高清版于2017年7月在PlayStation 4平台发售，史克威尔艾尼克斯在同年的10月底宣布PS4版的出货量已超过100万份。<ref>[http://www.vgtime.com/topic/873128.jhtml 《最终幻想12 黄道纪元》全球卖出100万份] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vgtime.com/topic/873128.jhtml |date=20200812095927 }}.游戏时光.2017-10-26.[2017-10-26].</ref>

《最终幻想XII》是第6款获得《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》满分的游戏，也是首款获满分的最终幻想游戏与PlayStation 2游戏。这还是松野泰己继《[[放浪冒险谭|放浪冒险谭]]》后又一款满分游戏。评论对游戏图形、剧本、游戏系统表示称赞，并赞扬游戏为系列增加了新要素<ref name="famitsu">{{cite web| author=Lumb, Jonathan| date=2006-03-08| title=FF XII Scores Perfect In Famitsu| publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]| url=http://1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3148658| accessdate=2006-08-13| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65Xa7sxAr?url=http://1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3148658| archivedate=2012-02-18}}</ref>。游戏甚至在西方发售前，就获得当地媒体的赞扬。《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》称赞了游戏全动态影像和游戏引擎画面的无缝切换<ref name="eurogamer">{{cite web| author=Albiges, Luke| date=2006-04-18| title=Final Fantasy XII review| publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]| url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/ir_ffxii_ps2| accessdate=2006-08-14| archive-date=2009-01-25| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090125070702/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/ir_ffxii_ps2| dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时游戏以其艺术风格获得“Top 10星期二”的第一名<ref>{{cite web| author=IGN Staff| date=2006-07-18| title=Top 10 Tuesday: Best Art in Videogames| publisher=IGN| url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/719/719602p1.html| accessdate=2006-08-14| archive-date=2012-06-21| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68ZnczwuF?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/719/719602p1.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Newtype USA》称《最终幻想XII》将游戏选为2006年11月“月度游戏”，杂志对其系统、图形、故事表示称赞，是“索尼平台史上的最佳RPG”<ref>{{cite web| author=Joynt, Patrick| date=2006-11-01| title=Newtype USA / Reviews / Final Fantasy XII| publisher=[[Newtype_(magazine)|Newtype]]| url=http://www.newtype-usa.com/reviews/index.php?itemid=342| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070521200034/http://www.newtype-usa.com/reviews/index.php?itemid=342| archivedate=2007-05-21| accessdate=2007-01-17| deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

GameSpot虽然称赞策略和执照系统是新颖而深入的角色控制方式，但也表示系统复杂困难、难以适应，对新手则尤甚。评论还批评间或乏味的来回折行。此外评论还特别称赞了“出色”的配音阵容<ref name="Gamespotreview">{{cite web|author=Kasavin, Greg|date=2006-10-31 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasy12/review.html |title=Final Fantasy XII for PlayStation 2 Review|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2007-03-04}}</ref>。IGN称赞游戏丰富的情节和艺术监督“深入了角色”。他还为“游戏自己玩自己”的批评做辩护，称策略系统少了玩家就不起作用。不过网站也称，虽然《最终幻想XII》“仍然非常强”，但原声是系列最无力的之一<ref name="IGNreview" />。

执行制作人[[河津秋敏|河津秋敏]]对《Fami通》的评分表示高兴，但他承认游戏并非完美；他认为故事未不满足部分爱好者的期望<ref>{{cite web | author=Wales, Matt | date=2006-10-26 | title=Square Talks Firsts for Final Fantasy XII | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/742/742013p1.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2007-06-28 | archive-date=2007-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070124114407/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/742/742013p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。河津还称[[PlayOnline|PlayOnline]]和《最终幻想战略版》团队成员间有创造性分歧，这是他对故事的无奈与遗憾<ref>{{cite web | author=Verlet, Nicolas | date=2006-10-24 | title=Interview : Akitoshi Kawazu (FF XII) | url=http://www.gamekult.com/articles/A0000052257/ | publisher=Gamekult.com | accessdate=2007-07-17 | language=fr | archive-date=2007-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715010333/http://www.gamekult.com/articles/A0000052257/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

