ws/2007/04/20/103,1177037473,70570,0,0.html |publisher=[[Fami通|Fami通]] |title=速報！　ファミ通ゲームアワード2006開催！　各受賞タイトルを一挙発表！ |date=2007-04-20 |accessdate=2010-03-20 |language=ja |archive-date=2012-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022014632/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/2007/04/20/103,1177037473,70570,0,0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本作在2006年度[[日本游戏大奖|日本游戏大奖]]摘得“大奖”和“优秀奖”，以及该年度PlayStation奖的“双白金奖”<ref name="japan_awards">{{cite web| url=http://awards.cesa.or.jp/2006/english/prizelist/2005-2006/index.html| publisher=Computer Entertainment Supplier's Association (CESA)| title=Awarded Games: Final Fantasy XII| accessdate=2010-01-19| archive-date=2011-05-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110519154206/http://awards.cesa.or.jp/2006/english/prizelist/2005-2006/index.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/20060726/psa.htm |language=ja |publisher=GAME Watch |title=SCEJ、「PlayStation Awards 2006」受賞タイトルを発表PS2「ファイナルファンタジーXII」がダブルプラチナプライズ |date=2006-07-26 |accessdate=2010-03-20 |archive-date=2012-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009162220/http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/20060726/psa.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jp.playstation.com/info/release/nr_20060725_awards.html |language=ja |publisher=[[Sony_Computer_Entertainment_Inc.|Sony Computer Entertainment Inc.]] |title=「PlayStation Awards 2006」受賞タイトルについて |date=2006-07-25 |accessdate=2010-03-20 |archive-date=2009-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090909234507/http://www.jp.playstation.com/info/release/nr_20060725_awards.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏因作为“日本原产产品与服务的杰出象征”，入选“新100日本样式”榜单<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/company/e/history/ |publisher=SQUARE ENIX |title=Corporate History |accessdate=2010-01-19 |archive-date=2007-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070530053804/http://www.square-enix.com/jp/company/e/history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=2006-01-19 |url=