==续作与再发行版==
=== 国际版黄道十二宫职业系统 ===

史克威尔艾尼克斯在2007年5月10日对外公开了游戏[[国际版|国际版]]《最终幻想XII国际版 黄道十二宫职业系统》<ref>{{cite web|title=スクウェア・エニックス、「SQUARE ENIX PARTY 2007」 プレカンファレンスミーティング開催 「ラスト レムナント」はPS3/Xbox 360で北米/日本同時発売|url=http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/20070510/sep.htm|accessdate=2012-02-04|date=2007-05-10|archive-date=2013-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618155318/http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/20070510/sep.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏作为最终幻想20周年纪念与[[伊瓦莉斯联盟|伊瓦莉斯联盟]]作品，于2007年8月9日在日本推出<ref>{{cite web| date=2007-05-14| title=Square Enix Party Press Conference Announcement| publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]| url=http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2007/0514_3/| accessdate=2007-07-14| archive-date=2007-05-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070517090253/http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2007/0514_3/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏将原版单一执照版改为12个执照版，每个执照版各对应一个星座与职业。游戏战斗系统也有调整，如玩家可以控制临时角色和召唤兽，按L1键可以加速游戏。此外游戏采用英语配音，支持16:9宽屏分辨率，同时收录北美版首卖时的附赠光碟。国际版新增有三种模式：“[[二周目|强模式]]”、“弱模式”（角色不获得经验）和“挑战模式”（玩家在100个地图中猎杀怪物，获得道具与金钱）<ref name="international">{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q2-2007/050907a.html |title=Final Fantasy IV Remake, XII International Announced |accessdate=2007-05-09 |author=Boulette, Bryan |date=2007-05-09 |publisher=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930030332/http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q2-2007/050907a.html |archivedate=2007年9月30日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ffworld.com/?rub=news&page=voir&id=764 |title=FFXII International: Plus d'infos (MàJ) |accessdate=2007-05-10 |author=KujaFFman |date=2007-05-10 |publisher=Final Fantasy World |language=fr |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bcop8ZNv?url=http://www.ffworld.com/?rub=news |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ffworld.com/?rub=news&page=voir&id=771 |title=FFXII International: Des détails |accessdate=2007-05-12 |author=KujaFFman |date=2007-05-12 |publisher=Final Fantasy World |language=fr |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BcopkR4W?url=http://www.ffworld.com/?rub=news |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| author=Hirohiko Niizumi| date=2007-05-03| title=Final Fantasy XII International Zodiac Job System| publisher=GameSpot| url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-fantasy-xii-international-zodiac-job-system-hands-on/1100-6170691/| accessdate=2007-05-29| archive-date=2015-09-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909025356/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-fantasy-xii-international-zodiac-job-system-hands-on/1100-6170691/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===归来之翼===
《最终幻想XII》的续作《[[最终幻想XII_归来之翼|最终幻想XII 归来之翼]]》于2007年在[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]发行，游戏讲述梵在原作情节结尾一年后的冒险<ref>{{cite web | author=IGN Staff | date=2006-09-21 | title=TGS 2006: Final Fantasy XII Update | url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/733/733945p1.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2006-09-21 | archive-date=2006-10-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061007025028/http://ds.ign.com/articles/733/733945p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。它和国际版《最终幻想XII》同属[[伊瓦莉斯联盟|伊瓦莉斯联盟]]四款作品之一<ref>{{cite web| author=Winkler, Chris| date=2006-12-13| title=Square Enix announces FF Tactics for the PSP and Another New FFT Game| publisher=RPGFan| url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1595.html| accessdate=2007-01-10| archive-date=2012-02-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223195249/http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1595.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===堡垒===
《[[堡垒_(未发行游戏)|堡垒]]》（{{lang|en|Fortress}}）原是由[[Grin|Grin]]开发的衍生动作冒险游戏，讲述《归来之翼》后伊瓦莉斯的故事，是一部“故事和产值都呈史诗规模”的游戏<ref>{{cite web | first=Andy | last=Robinson | title=Final Fantasy XII spin-off leaked | url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=231811 | publisher=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]] | date=2010-01-18 | accessdate=2010-01-19 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BcpG6Xgu?url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/231811/final-fantasy-xii-spin-off-leaked/ | archive-date=2012-10-23 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Albihn">{{cite web | first=Björn | last=Albihn | title=Björn Albihn - Character Artist | url=http://www.albihn.net/ | publisher= | date=2009-09-07 | accessdate=2009-09-22 | archive-date=2009-09-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090923050453/http://www.albihn.net/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。史克威尔艾尼克斯在开发六个月后，以品量问题为由取消项目并拒绝向Grin付费，此举致使Grin宣布破产<ref name="1UPFORT">{{cite web | first=Quillen | last=Dustin | title=GRIN Was Working on an Unannounced Final Fantasy Project | url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3175684 | publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | date=2009-08-20 | accessdate=2009-09-22 | archive-date=2012-10-23 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BcpHLnRN?url=http://www.1up.com/news/grin-working-unannounced-final-fantasy | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="GIFORT">{{cite web | first= | last= | title=GRIN's Final Fantasy spin-off still in development | url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/grins-final-fantasy-spin-off-still-in-development | publisher=GamesIndustry.biz | date=2009-09-21 | accessdate=2009-09-22 | archive-date=2010-01-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105070922/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/grins-final-fantasy-spin-off-still-in-development | dead-url=no }}</ref>。后有传言称作品交由其他工作室开发，但《归来之翼》总监[[鸟山求|鸟山求]]在E3 2011上正式宣布，作品“中止”开发并“永远不会发行”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.videogamer.com/news/final_fantasy_xii_spin-off_fortress_suspended.html |title=Final Fantasy XII spin-off Fortress 'suspended' |publisher=VideoGamer |accessdate=2011-07-04 |date=2011-06-09 |archive-date=2015-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120183824/http://www.videogamer.com/xbox360/final_fantasy_132/news/final_fantasy_xii_spin-off_fortress_suspended.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

